<li>Meta description generation with keyword inclusion</li>
<li>Internal link suggestions based on content relevance</li>
<li>Schema markup generation for rich results</li>
<li>Image alt text optimization</li>
<li>Readability and sentence length analysis</li>
</ul>
<p>These checks run automatically during production. The output is content that scores 80 to 95 on SEO audits before a human even touches it.</p>
